WEBVTT

1
00:01:36.555 --> 00:01:37.680
<font color="#fecb00">EMERGENCY OCCURRENCE</font>

2
00:01:37.681 --> 00:01:38.681
<font color="#fecb00">PLEASE STAY ALERT</font>

3
00:01:43.478 --> 00:01:44.812
<font color="#fecb00">EMERGENCY OCCURRENCE</font>

4
00:01:44.813 --> 00:01:46.565
<font color="#fecb00">PLEASE STAY ALERT</font>

5
00:02:02.247 --> 00:02:03.248
<font color="#fecb00">It's Lee Shaw!</font>

6
00:02:06.126 --> 00:02:07.920
<font color="#fecb00">They're headed to the south gate!</font>

7
00:02:08.211 --> 00:02:09.295
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Close the south gate!</i></font>

8
00:02:53.215 --> 00:02:55.425
<font color="#fecb00">He's coming back! Main entrance!</font>

9
00:18:55.427 --> 00:18:56.427
<font color="#fecb00">Passport.</font>

10
00:18:57.262 --> 00:18:58.263
<font color="#fecb00">Passport!</font>

11
00:19:54.194 --> 00:19:55.194
<font color="#fecb00">I told you</font>

12
00:19:55.195 --> 00:19:57.697
<font color="#fecb00">you would meet some really stupid people.</font>

13
00:19:57.698 --> 00:19:58.866
<font color="#fecb00">I know.</font>

14
00:21:13.482 --> 00:21:15.150
<font color="#fecb00">What did he tell you?</font>

15
00:21:16.693 --> 00:21:19.779
<font color="#fecb00">Some valuable data had been stolen.
We needed to retrieve it.</font>

16
00:21:19.780 --> 00:21:22.782
<font color="#fecb00">And did he mention that he had
no authorization to run</font>

17
00:21:22.783 --> 00:21:24.535
<font color="#fecb00">this rogue escapade of his?</font>

18
00:21:28.830 --> 00:21:30.457
<font color="#fecb00">I assumed...</font>

19
00:22:05.492 --> 00:22:06.493
<font color="#fecb00">This is confirmed?</font>

20
00:22:06.827 --> 00:22:07.828
<font color="#fecb00">All of them?</font>

21
00:22:11.748 --> 00:22:12.916
<font color="#fecb00">All right. stand by.</font>

22
00:26:49.067 --> 00:26:50.861
<font color="#fecb00">Let me go! Let me go!</font>

23
00:26:51.486 --> 00:26:52.486
<font color="#fecb00">I have to stop it!</font>

24
00:26:52.487 --> 00:26:53.572
<font color="#fecb00">Stop!!</font>

25
00:26:54.615 --> 00:26:56.157
<font color="#fecb00">Please don't do it!</font>

26
00:26:56.158 --> 00:26:57.283
<font color="#fecb00">You can't do this!</font>

27
00:26:57.284 --> 00:26:58.452
<font color="#fecb00">Please!</font>

28
00:39:53.227 --> 00:39:54.394
<font color="#fecb00">It landed.</font>

29
00:39:55.187 --> 00:39:56.355
<font color="#fecb00">Safely.</font>
